    {
      "chinese": "以農耕為主的親愛部落，「水」是最為重要且不可或缺的資源。濁水溪豐沛的水量是農民灌溉用水的絕佳來源，水中魚蝦亦可做為村民的食材，最為特別的資源是可以在部落河床上尋找金、玉、石共存的「龍紋石」。原石經過機器切割、琢磨、拋光後，會呈現出深綠、棕紅、深橙、鈦銀、金銅、翠綠、乳白、琥珀等美麗的色澤，深受雅石收藏家的喜愛。",
      "ab": "lanlamu na ṟagu’ pamuhyun ka alang Plngawan. use’ ka pu’ing kakayanux na ṟagu’. ramas caṟung na ṟagu’ ka luling mamutung hani, kelan na ucyux, balulung ni’un na ci’uli’ alang. syaw na luling, kelan na uṟati’ ramas taxan. maki’ ṟik na buna’iy ka king uṟi. kelan ka uṟati’ sun naha “longwunsu” babali’un gungasgas na kika’i la ga, pascex ci masinpayux ka iro’ ni. kelan na matanah, magaṟagu’, malabu’, muking, ramas caṟung taxan. kisli’ caṟung na ci’uli’ pakalahang ci uṟati’ uṟi.",
      "order": "2",
